{"tid":1541513,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「懶人包」政府4大行動 極度陰濕 仆街 卑鄙","createTime":"2019-09-04T14:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:27:56.000Z","uid":7971,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"199f6bc027b995c3336d65c902d801c012a361bc","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簡單講</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n1、撤回條例<br />\n美國人權法案 <br />\n有所阻礙 同 應受者變得失去相應名份 減少急切性<br />\n同時間幫中共buy time <br />\n<br />\n2、監警會加人<br />\n定心丸及籍口予警方及藍絲<br />\n<br />\n3、官員落區<br />\n流水社運轉為死水社運 有利政權打壓抗爭<br />\n<br />\n4、鼓勵學者獨立研究事件<br />\n學者研究為分化手段第一步<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長文分析</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一、撤回條例<br />\n<br />\n表面上，向大眾釋出善意，且經濟已經有明顯下降，淺黃中立嘅立場一定有所動搖。<br />\n<br />\n實際上，<br />\ni)國際以為香港人贏咗<br />\n因為外國人會知道場運動係反送中，遠遠多過5大訴求。<br />\n<br />\nii)回應美國人權法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">令人權法案變成無急切需要同出師名份有所減少，亦有向美國議員誤導成份</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二、監警會加人<br />\n<br />\n再次派定心丸予警，等佢哋覺得政府唔會對警有所出賣。其次可以又一機會俾籍口予藍絲 (下刪100字)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三、官員落區<br />\n<br />\n依點係最賤格 <br />\n抗爭由7月開始轉為流水式社運be water。<br />\n游擊戰下，抗爭者無需介意死守或執著某一個地方 成hit and run 令對方防佈成本提高，應對有所困難。落區後，抗爭者會易轉變為圍堵官員，對家就可以有所準備。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">政權張流水社運轉為死水社運，令我哋嘅位置之戰，由游擊成對碰，武力懸殊下 ，只會令政權更有利打擊</span><br />\n<br />\n四、鼓勵學者獨立研究事件<br />\n<br />\n一方面 以學者研究之名嘗試誤導民眾(無咩腦個班 c9 啊婆) 獨立調查研究等同委員會<br />\n<br />\n實際 其實係拉攏學者派別 同少部份和理非 <span style=\"color: orange;\">以學術方式成自我分化 最終可以預期到學者研究結果會想成 <br />\n以和平方式爭取表達 會遠遠好過暴力表達<br />\n成分化手段嘅其中一步</span>"},{"pid":"f53d83f1d2e54272cff21bf51b9a62f6069339fb","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ab27bc1be2d947102d5eb9ce68a246e23816264","tid":1541513,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f6fc651390217d5cec4d0fa7ba791e7ac7b8ab3","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99d0263072e7941e2fc484362cc623e27493847d","tid":1541513,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"林鄭又撚鳩我地喇！<br />\n立法會議事規則列明撤回法案只需「宣佈」，不需「動議」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dONuKS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dONuKS</a>"},{"pid":"52d9bca30aa089ea2f1c5ecd3744084654980091","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d72063f6a61e13f3d1e26cbf21949688638dfce","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ecdf7b64f0b4bb448ac8392a9f22decd9538b0a","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccbe112a5ab2eba9846096b5b18bf3844d4309ce","tid":1541513,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing 5 demands, not 1 less?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"600fe05b3ff7dc0fc9ac291c80ae878093e5dc26","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8c4014c3d85317522f924d90b35bb4b5bd7e0fc","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9f43faf63e717e4645c920bdfa19bae2b50d3af","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9519bffd37c36cf401ffa418f9d46d099eda7b42","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3353a5f68ab1e23c433360abeaf72ece05754c96","tid":1541513,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote><em>我們成長為自由人。 沒人可讓一個自由的人下跪。<br />\nWe grew up as free people.<br />\nNo one can make a free person kneel.</em><br />\n<strong><del>WINTER ON FIRE</del><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n《HONG KONG BE WATER》</span></strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、<span style=\"color: violet;\">民主人權法案</span>、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債 主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n提防 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美、德領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>這不單是 反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>流水革命 元年</ins></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"e2d21923b6ae85fe313079ee923a031a5988baf5","tid":1541513,"uid":211578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n8人離世<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0257be5fe868fbe8ed1770900f356e4045caca54","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b1b9a88fc9e740a3d4f3ad3d8ff21464c28fddf","tid":1541513,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"咁應該點"},{"pid":"09d2ead869b1bee601e4b7194008f2559a188dfe","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b1b9a88fc9e740a3d4f3ad3d8ff21464c28fddf","tid":1541513,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"咁應該點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"國際文宣 流水社運為主軸<br />\n雙普選為方針"},{"pid":"9bcbc05bed0137b74841eb07f0e4001a93866a36","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:22:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6a90b2dbc35149a2a4a2a1e860799f374fefba8","tid":1541513,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b1b9a88fc9e740a3d4f3ad3d8ff21464c28fddf","tid":1541513,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"咁應該點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c898966d91e983ca7757bdc02eac5e846bb7d4","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6a90b2dbc35149a2a4a2a1e860799f374fefba8","tid":1541513,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b1b9a88fc9e740a3d4f3ad3d8ff21464c28fddf","tid":1541513,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"咁應該點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe83c3b6995c968e4d1e0b4e37f04a031f94b50","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8e839313402888e11e56cd269aeb4258b99bc80","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"809672ea9414a510ff70bef1712602911fe482ea","tid":1541513,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab0d85c7f6b966379a5f73baa283003f3f024376","tid":1541513,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得其實五大訴求句口號已經變成我地弱點<br />\n<br />\n一嚟6月至今新加嘅訴求好難再入到屋(監控燈柱、解散警隊...）<br />\n<br />\n二嚟除真雙普選以外四大訴求，無論佢全盤接受定係提出閹割版，都只會係佢攻擊分化我地嘅手段<br />\n<br />\n我地必須要認清楚，場運動一早已經變咗民主革命，五大訴求只有成立到民選新政府先有用，推翻舊政制成立新制度先係我地目標，林鄭無論點回應做咩措拖都係偽命題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 美帝議員應該冇咁易誤導到，唔好睇低人地政治智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有高官落區，準備定垃圾桶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}